divs: Sighting DetailsI took a picture of an area from my backyard overlooking a field with trees over 1000 ft away because I have been seeing objects for a few days over the area. I got a photo of several ufo's some flying in a sort of pattern. Daylight at about 6 PM. No noise. Facing South.
